gin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "1668326", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<div class=\"container\"><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"crumbs\"><a href=\"/\">Home</a> \u203a About</nav></div>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "c044fb8", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "af5feca", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"page-hero\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">About Us</span>\n<h1>Booking software, made with a boutique's eye.</h1>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n<p class=\"lead\">Ivory Digital is a Manchester-based studio dedicated to one thing: giving bridal boutiques beautiful, dependable booking software they actually own.</p>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "ad7b2e2", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "c40ab0f", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section>\n<div class=\"container\" style=\"max-width:760px\">\n<p>Bridal is a business of first impressions and precious moments. Yet so many boutiques still juggle a paper diary, missed calls during fittings, and clunky third-party booking widgets that look nothing like their brand \u2014 and quietly charge a fee on every booking.</p>\n<p>We built Ivory Digital to change that. We create a private, elegant booking system for each boutique: a customer-facing website that feels like a natural extension of your shop, paired with a powerful behind-the-scenes diary that keeps your team calm and in control. No generic widget, no per-booking commission \u2014 just software that works the way you do.</p>\n<h2 style=\"margin-top:2rem\">How we work</h2>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n<p>Every system is bespoke. We learn how your boutique runs \u2014 your appointment types, your questions, your hours and how many brides you can see at once \u2014 and shape the software around it. Then we brand it to you, host it on your domain, and look after it with a simple maintenance package so you can focus on your brides.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container grid grid-3\" style=\"margin-top:2.2rem\">\n<div class=\"card\"><h3>Bespoke</h3><p>Built around your boutique \u2014 never a one-size-fits-all template.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><h3>Owned by you</h3><p>Your brand, your data, your system \u2014 not rented from a platform.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><h3>Looked after</h3><p>UK-based hosting, backups, updates and friendly support.</p></div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "cf846fa", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "91eae70", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"cta-band\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">Work With Us</span>\n<h2>Let's build something beautiful.</h2>\n<p>We'd love to hear about your boutique and how we can help.</p>\n<div class=\"btn-row\" style=\"justify-content:center\"><a class=\"btn btn-light\" href=\"/contact/\">Get in Touch</a></div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "a23f38a", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "35c55d3", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<footer class=\"site-footer\">\n<div class=\"container footer-grid\">\n<div class=\"footer-brand\"><img alt=\"Ivory Digital\" class=\"footer-logo\" src=\"__IVORY_BASE__/assets/img/logo.png\"/><p>Booking systems for bridal boutiques &amp; StudioApp client galleries for wedding photographers, across the United Kingdom.</p></div>\n<div><h4>Explore</h4><ul><li><a href=\"/booking-system/\">Booking System</a></li><li><a href=\"/studioapp/\">StudioApp</a></li><li><a href=\"/web-design-seo/\">Web Design &amp; SEO</a></li><li><a href=\"/locations/\">Booking by Location</a></li><li><a href=\"/pricing/\">Pricing</a></li><li><a href=\"/about/\">About</a></li><li><a href=\"/faq/\">FAQ</a></li><li><a href=\"/contact/\">Contact</a></li></ul></div>\n<div><h4>Get in Touch</h4><ul><li><a href=\"mailto:sales@ivorydigital.uk\">sales@ivorydigital.uk</a></li><li><a href=\"tel:+447712117357\">+44 7712 117357</a></li><li>220 Ashurst Road,<br/>Manchester, M22 5AX</li></ul></div>\n</div>\n<div class